RUSTPROOF AND DURABLE: Made of premium stainless steel materials, LIVOD over the sink drying rack is very durable and free of rust. The 3- tier dish rack over sink have passed a 24 hours salt test, you don’t have to worry about the safety and health issue during the using. With a weight-bearing of up to 200lbs, it also saves your precious countertop space by making full use of the room over the sink. It is a real durable over sink dish drying rack stainless steel for a long term use.

LARGE CAPACITY EXPANDABLE LENGTH: The size of the dish drying rack over the sink is adjustable, the Min width is 29.1” and Max width is 37.4”, can meet both single and double sinks in your kitchen, 2 layers large shelves and a full range of accessories can help you storage a lot of kitchen items, it is great gift for both you and your kitchen-loving friends.

SIMPLE ASSEMBLY & EASY CLEANING: LIVOD above sink dish drying rack is punched with accurate screw holes, and the screws and hex key come well kept in an extra bag, so you can easily assemble it with our user manual. All attachments can be easily detached to clean, wiping them with only a damp towel. Add to your cart now, then you will have a perfect over sink dish drainer for your kitchen.

MEASURE THE SIZE BEFORE PURCHASE: It is important to accurately measure three values before your order: the width of the space where the kitchen sink is located, the height of the faucet, and the distance between the bottom of the cabinet and the countertop. LIVOD provide lifetime after-sales service for this large kitchen sink dish drying rack.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely love this 3 tier drying rack from LIVOD! It has been life changing!! It freed up my 2nd kitchen sink as my other drying rack was always in there. It's great having two sinks clean and clear of dishes during the day. It is very sturdy, even the top rack holds my big cast iron skillet without wobbling at all! There is a spot for all my dishes and odd shaped items with no issue! I have had it for a few months now and still no rust. This rack is made from quality materials. I looked at other, cheaper versions, but ultimately decided to pay a bit more for better quality and stability as life is too short for cheap junk! I am so glad I did, as this rack is definitely worth it. I would recommend this specific dish rack to my family and friends looking to purchase a similar item. Thanks LIVOD for going above and beyond with your products and their amazing quality!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars For the price, good hardware would have been nice.
reviews.reviewText: The first thing you should do when you open the package is throw away the hardware bag which includes all the screws, nuts and two little wrenches. They are absolute junk. Go to the hardware store and buy some nice screws and nuts. For $130, this absolutely irks me. The shelf holes do not line up in the front. I ended up using a clamp to spread the shelves apart far enough to get the two front bolts in both shelves. They were off by at least 1/4 inch. I do not notice the shelves being out of level with the eye test.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very difficult to put together very and I am not a novice .
reviews.reviewText: This is a quality piece of equipment however, it is very difficult to put together. It truly is the parts that do come with it like the key cheap had to go out and buy a whole new set of keys, but the unit itself is very stable and very industrial looking, if you’re a beginner do not tackle this you’ll never get it done. Seriously there’s a lot of times it was so tight to where you had to put in the screws in the nuts they could’ve designed it a little better.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This product is advertised as stainless steel. If it is, it is very thin and austenitic (non-ferromagnetic) stainless steel.The middle, when extended, bows out.The assembly instructions are poor though assembly is not overly difficult.Some screws and nuts are very difficult to tighten properly due to poor design. Accessing the location to tighten the screws/nuts is a challenge.Some of the screws are different sizes but the instructions lump them all in together.Overall, this isn’t worth it even with the lightning deal discount. I wanted something sturdy and long lasting. This product is definitely NOT it.
